											style="background-color: initial; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-transform: inherit; white-space: inherit; word-spacing: normal; caret-color: auto;">The
											ability to display banner alerts and notifications was a feature made more popular by the pandemic. It seemed like every website you
